title: Johnny Rebel
description:
Johnny Rebel, written by Caitlin Tegart. Stone Cold Fox at Maude Night, UCBTNY, May 19, 2008.

Starring Sean Clements, Scott Courlander, D'Arcy Erokan, Fran Gillespie, Nate Lang, Cody Melton, and David C. White. Directed by Neil W. Casey.
